reviewText:
On Youtube I can find Helene Fischer singing in English "The Power of Love" and "My Heart Will Go On." But I can't find any Cd's with her
singing the mentioned songs in English. But this Dvd has her singing "My Heart Will Go On" in English. I believe she has every bit the voice of
Cline Dion if not better. I fully enjoyed this Dvd, and have already watched it twice.
